citations:
    citation-agot-tyrion-ix:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Tyrion IX"
            text_from_source: "Tyrion, have you forgotten your courtesies? Kindly acquaint us with our … honored guests … The fair maid is Chella daughter of Cheyk of the Black Ears … Shagga son of Dolf is the one who looks like Casterly Rock with hair."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Tyrion arrives at Lord Tywin's camp at the crossroads inn with his mountain clan allies: Chella daughter of Cheyk (Black Ears), Shagga son of Dolf and Conn son of Coratt (Stone Crows), Ulf son of Umar (Moon Brothers), Timett son of Timett (Burned Men, a red hand), and sellsword Bronn. Ser Flement Brax is identified as commanding outriders. Ser Kevan Lannister is present. Tyrion reports Robert dead and Joffrey on the throne. Tywin reports: Jaime has defeated Lords Vance and Piper at Golden Tooth, captured Edmure Tully, besieges Riverrun; Lady Whent yielded Harrenhal; Raventree fell. Ser Gregor Clegane burned out Pipers and Brackens. Ser Addam Marbrand commands Lannister outriders. News arrives that Robb Stark's host is moving south. Tywin orders march to engage them. The clans agree to ride with the Lannisters."
